Interview Follow-up
                
                  Why is
                  
                          LinkedList.get(500)
                  
                  not O(1)?
                  
                  Because nodes are not contiguous.
                  
                  Memory looks like:
  
                                Node
                                
                                ↓
                              
                              Node
                              
                              ↓
                              
                              Node
                              
                              ↓
                              
                              Node

          To reach node 500,

              Java must visit  499 nodes

        Therefore   :O(n)



